<dl>
    <dt>Launch an application from the shell</dt>
        <dd>Application shall raise to the foreground</dd>
    <dt>Go to the launcher and launch a different application</dt>
        <dd>Application shall raise to the foreground</dd>
    <dt>Go to the Application Lens</dt>
        <dd>The two applications that were open shall be displayed and rendered in Running apps</dd>
    <dt>Hold your finger at a running app to display the X (close) icon</dt>
        <dd>A close icon shall be displayed on the Running apps</dd>
    <dt>Close the first application that was open</dt>
        <dd>After the application is closed, the shell shall remain in view</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
